{"type":"message","id":"7e1e97ae","parentId":"e24033e9","timestamp":"2026-03-31T08:23:20.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config updated and restarting. Now here's how dispatching works:\n\n**The Dispatch System — How You Use It:**\n\nJust tell me what you want done and I'll route it to the right agent. Or be explicit:\n\n- *\"Uriel, build the OCR endpoint\"* → I spawn Uriel as a sub-agent, he codes it autonomously, reports back\n- *\"Zadkiel, redesign the dashboard\"* → Zadkiel runs the UI/UX work\n- *\"Gabriel, write the pitch deck copy\"* → Gabriel handles it\n- *\"Do X, Y, Z\"* → I figure out who does what and dispatch in parallel\n\n**Agent Dispatch Map:**\n- 🔥 **Uriel** → Coding, dev, validation, testing\n- 🛠️ **Zadkiel** → UI/UX, product design, quality\n- 📣 **Gabriel** → Content, marketing, copy\n- 🤝 **Raguel** → Outreach, relationships\n- 🧭 **Rafael** → Strategy, coordination\n- ⚖️ **Samael** → Security, challenge assumptions\n- 🔮 **Sarael** → Synthesis, structured analysis\n- 💸 **Azrael** → Finance, cost tracking\n- 🛡️ **Remiel** → Legal, compliance\n- 🔮 **Metis** → Research, competitor intel\n\n**What you'll see:** I'll tell you \"Dispatched Uriel to [task]\" → when he's done, I'll forward the result to you. You can also ask me \"what's Uriel working on?\" anytime to check status.\n\nWanna test it? Give me a task to dispatch."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":411,"cacheRead":77302,"cacheWrite":3222,"totalTokens":80936,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.010275000000000001,"cacheRead":0.038651,"cacheWrite":0.020137500000000003,"total":0.0690685}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774945358330}}
