{"type":"message","id":"41d6207d","parentId":"083ebdd3","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:14:52.018Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHmm, tergantung maksudnya yang mana:\n\n**Yang bisa gw bantu:**\n- Research airdrop opportunities — cari project mana yang lagi buka airdrop, syaratnya apa, timeline-nya kapan\n- Track eligibility criteria — monitor wallet activity requirements, social tasks, testnet participation\n- Compile info dari Twitter/X — siapa yang nge-leak alpha, project mana yang confirmed airdrop\n- Bikin spreadsheet tracking — project, status, deadline, tasks done/pending\n\n**Yang nggak bisa gw lakuin langsung:**\n- Connect wallet / sign transactions — gw nggak punya akses ke wallet kamu\n- Interact on-chain — deploy, swap, bridge, mint NFT\n- Auto-like/retweet/post di X — gw bisa *draft* content tapi nggak bisa login & execute di account kamu\n\n**Tapi** kalau yang dimaksud \"garap airdrop di X\" itu soal farming social tasks (follow, like, retweet, quote tweet project-project tertentu) — gw bisa bantu:\n1. Riset project mana yang worth it di-farm\n2. Draft semua tweet/quote tweet yang perlu kamu post\n3. Track progress — task mana yang udah, mana yang belum\n4. Alert kalau ada deadline atau snapshot date\n\nMau gw riset dulu project apa yang lagi hot buat airdrop farming sekarang?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":358,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":93703,"totalTokens":94064,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00895,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.58564375,"total":0.59460875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774959278806}}
