), etc.)\n- Keep it simple and clean\n- Test that the endpoints work\n\nLook at the existing settings panel code in index.html to match the style. The settings tab has sections for model selection, theme, etc — add the allowlist section there.","runTimeoutSeconds":600}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":649,"cacheRead":99020,"cacheWrite":480,"totalTokens":100152,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.016225,"cacheRead":0.04951,"cacheWrite":0.003,"total":0.06875}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774959465365}}
