{"type":"message","id":"5b38dd27","parentId":"b4900b84","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:48:59.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_wsNvDQYA3vD5Qp6MpW2hOR","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/magi-v2/frontend/settings/index.html","offset":80,"limit":100}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":103,"cacheRead":109197,"cacheWrite":169,"totalTokens":109470,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.002575,"cacheRead":0.054598499999999994,"cacheWrite":0.0010562500000000001,"total":0.058234749999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774961335671}}
{"type":"message","id":"b89df1ad","parentId":"5b38dd27","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:48:59.344Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_wsNvDQYA3vD5Qp6MpW2hOR","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":".agent-controls{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0}\n\n/* Presets */\n.preset-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px}\n.preset{padding:10px 8px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--glass);cursor:pointer;text-align:center;transition:all .2s;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text2)}\n.preset:hover{border-color:rgba(99,102,241,.2);background:rgba(99,102,241,.04)}\n.preset.active{border-color:rgba(99,102,241,.4);background:rgba(99,102,241,.08);color:var(--primary)}\n.preset-icon{font-size:16px;margin-bottom:4px}\n\n/* Mode buttons (Eco/Standard/Max) */\n.mode-btns{display:flex;gap:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border-radius:8px;padding:3px}\n.mode-btn{padding:6px 12px;border:none;border-radius:6px;background:none;color:var(--text3);font-size:10px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all .2s}\n.mode-btn.active{background:rgba(99,102,241,.12);color:var(--primary)}\n.mode-btn:hover:not(.active){background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}\n\n/* Cron list */\n.cron-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03)}\n.cron-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}\n.cron-expr{font-family:'SF Mono',Monaco,monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--primary);background:rgba(99,102,241,.06);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0}\n.cron-cmd{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);flex:1;min-width:0;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}\n\n/* User row */\n.user-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03)}\n.user-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}\n.user-avatar{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(99,102,241,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);flex-shrink:0}\n.user-info{flex:1;min-width:0}\n.user-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:600}\n.user-role{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3)}\n\n/* Plugin grid */\n.plug-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:8px}\n.plug{padding:12px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--glass);text-align:center;transition:all .2s}\n.plug-icon{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:4px}\n.plug-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:600}\n.plug-status{font-size:9px;color:var(--accent);margin-top:2px}\n\n/* Toast */\n.toast{position:fixed;bottom:20px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(80px);background:rgba(14,18,36,.95);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);padding:10px 20px;border-radius:var(--r);font-size:12px;z-index:999;backdrop-filter:blur(20px);transition:transform .3s var(--ease);pointer-events:none}\n.toast.show{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}\n\n/* Responsive */\n@media(max-width:500px){\n  .page{padding:20px 14px 60px}\n  .preset-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}\n  .agent-controls select{min-width:100px}\n  .mode-btns{flex-wrap:wrap}\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"page\">\n\n  <div class=\"hdr\">\n    <a href=\"/dashboard/\" title=\"Back to Hub\" style=\"text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:700\"><span style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#34d399,#22d3ee);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent\">✦ MAGI</span></a>\n    <h1>Settings</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Global Mode -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"cpu\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Global Model Mode</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Switch all agents to a different cost/performance tier at once.</div>\n    <div class=\"mode-btns\" id=\"modeBtns\">\n      <button class=\"mode-btn\" data-mode=\"eco\" onclick=\"setGlobalMode('eco')\">Eco</button>\n      <button class=\"mode-btn active\" data-mode=\"standard\" onclick=\"setGlobalMode('standard')\">Standard</button>\n      <button class=\"mode-btn\" data-mode=\"max\" onclick=\"setGlobalMode('max')\">Max Logic</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Intensity -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"gauge\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Intensity Control</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Set how detailed each agent responds. 1 = ultra-concise, 10 = exhaustive deep-dive.</div>\n    <div class=\"preset-grid\" id=\"presets\"></div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"row-left\"><div class=\"row-name\">Global Override</div><div class=\"row-desc\">Apply same intensity to all agents</div></div>\n      <div class=\"row-right\">\n        <div class=\"slider-wrap\">\n          <input type=\"range\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" value=\"5\" id=\"globalSlider\" oninput=\"setGlobalIntensity(+this.value)\">\n          <span class=\"slider-val\" id=\"globalVal\">5</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"agentIntensity\" style=\"margin-top:8px\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Agent Configuration -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"brain\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Agent Configuration</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Set the AI model for each agent. Higher tier = smarter but more expensive.</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px;padding:10px 12px;background:rgba(99,102,241,.04);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,.1);border-radius:8px\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text2);white-space:nowrap\">Set all agents to:</span>\n      <select id=\"bulkModelSelect\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:160px\">\n        <option value=\"\" disabled selected>— Choose model —</option>\n      </select>\n      <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"applyBulkModel()\">Apply All</button>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"agentConfig\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Users & Access -->\n\n[449 more lines in file. Use offset=180 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774961339339}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a6412d2","parentId":"b89df1ad","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:49:03.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_PJkrpoX9gEJc9XqEiy9Toz","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":180,"path":"/home/openclaw/magi-v2/frontend/settings/index.html"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":103,"cacheRead":109366,"cacheWrite":2225,"totalTokens":111695,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.002575,"cacheRead":0.054682999999999995,"cacheWrite":0.01390625,"total":0.07116924999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774961339345}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3fb771b","parentId":"1a6412d2","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:49:03.284Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_PJkrpoX9gEJc9XqEiy9Toz","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"users\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Users & Access</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Manage who can access MAGI.</div>\n    <div id=\"userList\"></div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px\">\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"newUserName\" placeholder=\"Display name\">\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"newUserUsername\" placeholder=\"Username\">\n      <input type=\"password\" id=\"newUserPassword\" placeholder=\"Password\">\n      <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"createUser()\">Add User</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Guest Access -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"link\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Guest Access</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Share read-only links with limited agent access.</div>\n    <div id=\"guestList\"></div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px\">\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"guestName\" placeholder=\"Guest name (e.g. Kenny)\">\n      <div id=\"guestAgentPicker\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin:4px 0\"></div>\n      <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"createGuest()\">Create Guest Link</button>\n      <div id=\"guestResult\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);word-break:break-all\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Telegram -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"send\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Telegram Control</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Send messages through agent Telegram bots.</div>\n    <div id=\"tgStatus\" style=\"margin-bottom:10px\"></div>\n    <select id=\"tgAgent\" style=\"margin-bottom:8px\"></select>\n    <textarea id=\"tgMessage\" placeholder=\"Type a message...\" rows=\"3\"></textarea>\n    <div class=\"btn-row\" style=\"margin-top:8px\">\n      <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"sendTelegram(true)\">Send &amp; Forward</button>\n      <button class=\"btn btn-sm\" onclick=\"sendTelegram(false)\">Reply Only</button>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"tgReply\" style=\"display:none;margin-top:10px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px;line-height:1.6\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- WhatsApp -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"message-circle\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:#25D366\"></i> WhatsApp Control</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Send messages via WhatsApp through OpenClaw gateway.</div>\n    <div id=\"waStatus\" style=\"margin-bottom:10px\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 10px;background:rgba(37,211,102,.08);border:1px solid rgba(37,211,102,.15);border-radius:8px;font-size:11px;color:#25D366\">\n        <i data-lucide=\"check-circle\" style=\"width:13px;height:13px\"></i> Connected\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:8px\">\n      <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:4px;display:block\">Recipient</label>\n      <select id=\"waRecipient\" style=\"width:100%;margin-bottom:0\">\n        <option value=\"+6285133221170\">Richard (+62851...170)</option>\n        <option value=\"+6285845730981\">Mr Salbi (+62858...981)</option>\n      </select>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:8px\">\n      <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:4px;display:block\">Send as Agent</label>\n      <select id=\"waAgent\" style=\"width:100%\"></select>\n    </div>\n    <textarea id=\"waMessage\" placeholder=\"Type a message...\" rows=\"3\"></textarea>\n    <div class=\"btn-row\" style=\"margin-top:8px\">\n      <button class=\"btn btn-sm\" style=\"background:rgba(37,211,102,.12);border-color:rgba(37,211,102,.2);color:#25D366\" onclick=\"sendWhatsApp()\">\n        <i data-lucide=\"send\" style=\"width:13px;height:13px\"></i> Send via WhatsApp\n      </button>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"waReply\" style=\"display:none;margin-top:10px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px;line-height:1.6\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Cron Jobs -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"clock\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Cron Jobs</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Scheduled tasks — standup, reports, monitoring.</div>\n    <div id=\"cronList\"></div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:10px;display:flex;gap:6px\">\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"cronExpr\" placeholder=\"0 8 * * *\" style=\"max-width:120px\">\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"cronCmd\" placeholder=\"Command...\" style=\"flex:1\">\n      <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"addCron()\">Add</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Plugins -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"puzzle\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Plugins</div>\n    <div class=\"plug-grid\" id=\"plugGrid\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Document Vault -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"folder-up\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Document Upload</div>\n    <div class=\"card-desc\">Upload files for agents to reference — PDF, CSV, TXT, images.</div>\n    <div style=\"border:1px dashed var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text3);font-size:11px;transition:all .2s\" \n         onclick=\"document.getElementById('docFile').click()\"\n         ondragover=\"event.preventDefault();this.style.borderColor='rgba(99,102,241,.3)'\"\n         ondragleave=\"this.style.borderColor='var(--border)'\"\n         ondrop=\"handleDrop(event)\">\n      Click or drag files here · PDF, CSV, TXT, MD, Images\n    </div>\n    <input type=\"file\" id=\"docFile\" style=\"display:none\" accept=\".pdf,.csv,.txt,.md,.jpg,.png\" multiple onchange=\"uploadFiles(this.files)\">\n    <div id=\"docList\" style=\"margin-top:8px\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Appearance -->\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\"><i data-lucide=\"palette\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--primary)\"></i> Appearance</div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"row-left\"><div class=\"row-name\">Language</div></div>\n      <div class=\"row-right\">\n        <select id=\"langSel\" onchange=\"setLang(this.value)\">\n          <option value=\"en\">English</option>\n          <option value=\"id\">Bahasa Indonesia</option>\n        </select>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"row-left\"><div class=\"row-name\">Theme</div><div class=\"row-desc\">Dark is the only way</div></div>\n      <div class=\"row-right\">\n        <select disabled><option>Dark</option></select>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Danger Zone -->\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-color:rgba(239,68,68,.12)\">\n    <div class=\"card-h\" style=\"color:var(--err)\"><i data-lucide=\"alert-triangle\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--err)\"></i> Danger Zone</div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"row-left\"><div class=\"row-name\">Clear All Sessions</div><div class=\"row-desc\">Delete all chat history</div></div>\n      <div class=\"row-right\"><button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"clearSessions()\">Clear</button></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"row-left\"><div class=\"row-name\">Reset Intensity</div><div class=\"row-desc\">Reset all agents to default (5)</div></div>\n      <div class=\"row-right\"><button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"resetIntensity()\">Reset</button></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"toast\" id=\"toast\"></div>\n\n<script>\nconst API = '/api'\nconst COUNCIL_API = '/council-api'\nlet A = {}, intensity = {}, models = {}, modelOverrides = {}, defaultModel = ''\n\nfunction toast(msg) {\n  const t = document.getElementById('toast')\n  t.textContent = msg; t.classList.add('show')\n  setTimeout(() => t.classList.remove('show'), 2500)\n}\n\n// ── Agents & Intensity ──────────────────────\nasync function loadAgents() {\n  try {\n    const r = await fetch(API + '/agents')\n    const d = await r.json()\n    A = d.agents || {}\n    renderAgentConfig()\n    renderAgentIntensity()\n    buildTgSelect()\n    buildGuestPicker()\n    buildWAAgentPicker()\n  } catch (e) { console.error('agents:', e) }\n}\n\nasync function loadIntensity() {\n  try {\n    const r = await fetch(API + '/intensity')\n    intensity = await r.json()\n    renderAgentIntensity()\n    renderPresets()\n  } catch (e) { console.error('intensity:', e) }\n}\n\nfunction renderPresets() {\n  const presets = [\n    { id: 'full', icon: 'flame', name: 'Full' },\n    { id: 'focus', icon: 'target', name: 'Focus' },\n    { id: 'quiet', icon: 'volume-x', name: 'Quiet' },\n    { id: 'balanced', icon: 'scale', name: 'Balanced' }\n  ]\n  document.getElementById('presets').innerHTML = presets.map(p =>\n    `<div class=\"preset\" onclick=\"applyPreset('${p.id}')\"><div class=\"preset-icon\"><i data-lucide=\"${p.icon}\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px\"></i></div>${p.name}</div>`\n  ).join('')\n  lucide.createIcons()\n}\n\nasync function applyPreset(id) {\n  try {\n    await fetch(API + '/intensity/preset', { method: 'PUT', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify({ preset: id }) })\n    await loadIntensity()\n    toast('✅ Preset \"' + id + '\" applied')\n  } catch (e) { toast('❌ Failed') }\n}\n\nfunction renderAgentIntensity() {\n  const el = document.getElementById('agentIntensity')\n  const sorted = Object.entries(A).sort((a, b) => (a[1].order || 0) - (b[1].order || 0))\n  el.innerHTML = sorted.map(([id, a]) => {\n    const val = (intensity[id] || 5)\n    return `<div class=\"agent-row\">\n      <span class=\"agent-dot\" style=\"background:${a.color}\"></span>\n\n[249 more lines in file. Use offset=380 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774961343280}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a1b74bd","parentId":"a3fb771b","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:49:22.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good, I can see the structure. Now let me dispatch Uriel to do all three tasks at once:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_JD801ZvFvJZZObJRKrrETI","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"uriel","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":600,"task":"Three tasks to do:\n\n## Task 1: Add WhatsApp Allowlist Manager to MAGI v2 Settings\n\nThe MAGI v2 settings page is at: /home/openclaw/magi-v2/frontend/settings/index.html\nThe backend (MAGI v2) is at: /home/openclaw/magi-v2/ — check for server.js or similar.\nThe MAGI v2 API base is /magi2-api (proxied to port 3002).\n\nAdd a \"WhatsApp Allowlist\" card section to the settings page. It should:\n- Show current allowed numbers from OpenClaw config (channels.whatsapp.allowFrom)\n- Let user add new numbers (with auto-format: 08xxx → +628xxx, 62xxx → +62xxx)\n- Let user remove numbers (with confirm)\n- Show success/error feedback via the existing toast() function\n- Match the existing card style (use .card, .card-h, .card-desc, .row classes)\n\nBackend endpoints needed (add to MAGI v2 server):\n- GET /wa-allowlist → returns {ok, allowFrom: [...]}\n- POST /wa-allowlist → add number {number: \"+62xxx\"}\n- DELETE /wa-allowlist → remove number {number: \"+62xxx\"}\n\nThese endpoints should read/write /home/openclaw/.openclaw/openclaw.json (JSON5 format — use json5 package, install if needed). After changes, run: require('child_process').exec('openclaw gateway restart')\n\nPlace the allowlist card BEFORE the \"Danger Zone\" card in the settings page.\n\n## Task 2: Update Dashboard MAGI Link\n\nIn /var/www/dashboard/index.html, change the MAGI button link from /council to /magi2\nYou'll need sudo to write to /var/www/dashboard/ — use: sudo cp approach or sudo tee.\n\n## Task 3: Remove /council Caddy Route\n\nIn /etc/caddy/Caddyfile, remove the @council route block:\n```\n@council path /council /council/*\nhandle @council {\n    root * /home/openclaw/council-room/frontend\n    rewrite * /index.html\n    file_server\n    header Cache-Control \"no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate\"\n}\n```\n\nThen reload caddy: sudo systemctl reload caddy\n\nDo NOT remove the @councilapi route — that's the backend API and still needed.\n\nAfter all tasks, restart pm2 for magi-v2: pm2 restart magi-v2"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":742,"cacheRead":111591,"cacheWrite":3428,"totalTokens":115762,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.01855,"cacheRead":0.0557955,"cacheWrite":0.021425,"total":0.0957755}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774961343285}}
