{"type":"message","id":"3e27a292","parentId":"a30a2713","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:58:43.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nD&D web app ya? Oke, tergantung scope yang kamu mau. Let me break it down dari essential sampai nice-to-have:\n\n**🎯 Core (Must Have):**\n1. **Character Sheet Builder** — create/edit characters, stats (STR/DEX/CON/INT/WIS/CHA), race, class, level, HP, AC, skills, saving throws\n2. **Dice Roller** — d4, d6, d8, d10, d12, d20, d100, with modifiers, advantage/disadvantage\n3. **Campaign/Session Manager** — create campaigns, invite players, track sessions\n4. **Initiative Tracker** — combat order, add/remove combatants, next turn button\n\n**⚔️ Combat & Gameplay:**\n5. **Spell Book** — searchable spell list, prepared spells, spell slots tracker\n6. **Inventory Manager** — items, weight, attunement, equipped/unequipped\n7. **HP & Condition Tracker** — damage/heal, temp HP, death saves, conditions (stunned, prone, etc.)\n8. **Combat Log** — history of rolls, damage, actions\n\n**🗺️ DM Tools:**\n9. **Monster/NPC Database** — searchable bestiary, custom NPCs, stat blocks\n10. **Encounter Builder** — CR calculator, drag monsters in, difficulty rating\n11. **Battle Map** — grid-based map, tokens, fog of war, movement\n12. **Session Notes** — per-session notes, shared/private, timeline\n\n**👥 Multiplayer/Social:**\n13. **Real-time Sync** — WebSocket, semua player lihat update live\n14. **Party Dashboard** — DM bisa lihat semua character sheets sekaligus\n15. **Chat/Voice** — in-app chat, or integrate Discord\n16. **Shared Dice Rolls** — semua orang lihat hasil roll\n\n**🤖 AI-Enhanced (Differentiator):**\n17. **AI DM Assistant** — generate encounters, NPCs, plot hooks, descriptions\n18. **AI Lore Generator** — world-building, town descriptions, tavern names\n19. **Rules Lookup** — tanya \"how does grapple work?\" → AI jawab with SRD reference\n20. **AI Character Backstory Generator**\n\n**📊 Extra:**\n21. **Level Up Wizard** — guided leveling, auto-calculate HP, new features\n22. **Loot Generator** — random treasure tables\n23. **World Map Builder** — hex/region map with pins\n24. **Character Art Gallery** — upload/generate portraits\n\n---\n\n**Rekomendasi gw — start dengan MVP:**\n- Character Sheet + Dice Roller + Initiative Tracker + Spell Book\n- Itu udah usable buat session pertama\n- Tambahin fitur seiring pemakaian\n\nMau mulai dari yang mana? Atau kamu punya vision spesifik buat web D&D-nya? (Personal use, atau mau di-launch ke publik?)"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":732,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":125569,"totalTokens":126304,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0183,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.78480625,"total":0.80312125}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774961903981}}
