{"type":"message","id":"656c5e22","parentId":"00b5776a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:59:19.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBuku 24 — maksudnya **D&D 2024 (revised/updated rules)**? Yang Player's Handbook 2024, Dungeon Master's Guide 2024, Monster Manual 2024?\n\nAtau \"buku 24\" itu reference ke sesuatu yang spesifik di circle D&D Indonesia? \n\nKasih tau biar gw bisa pastiin rules engine dan referensi yang dipake bener."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":109,"cacheRead":125569,"cacheWrite":893,"totalTokens":126574,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.002725,"cacheRead":0.0627845,"cacheWrite":0.00558125,"total":0.07110575}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774961954140}}
