{"type":"message","id":"26f82147","parentId":"3945f0f5","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:59:43.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAh oke, jadi ini buat **angkringan** kamu — kayak companion app buat D&D night di warung? Biar pemain yang dateng bisa pake bareng gitu?\n\nBiar gw paham lebih jelas:\n- Ini buat **satu meja/group** yang main bareng di angkringan?\n- Kamu yang jadi **DM** atau player?\n- Berapa orang biasanya yang main?\n- Mau diakses dari **HP** (mobile-first)?\n- Perlu **login per player** atau cukup satu device shared?\n\nDan soal rules 2024 — gw dispatch Metis buat riset dulu perubahan rules 2024 vs 5e lama biar rules engine-nya akurat. Sementara itu kasih tau gw scope-nya ya, biar begitu riset selesai langsung bisa mulai build."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":126745,"totalTokens":126982,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00585,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.79215625,"total":0.79802125}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774961974091}}
