{"type":"message","id":"d2003a1c","parentId":"e0d2c600","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:00:33.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGot it. Jadi:\n- Kamu **player**, ada DM sendiri\n- **Desktop-first** (tapi tetap responsive)\n- **Login pake PIN** (simple, no email/password ribet)\n- Rules **D&D 2024** (PHB 2024)\n- Buat **angkringan kamu** — private group\n\nGw mulai build ya. MVP dulu:\n\n**Phase 1 — Core:**\n1. ✅ PIN-based login (DM bikin room, kasih PIN ke player)\n2. ✅ Character Sheet (2024 rules — new species, classes, backgrounds)\n3. ✅ Dice Roller (shared, semua orang lihat)\n4. ✅ Initiative Tracker\n5. ✅ Spell Book (2024 spell list)\n\nGw dispatch Uriel buat build, Metis buat riset rules 2024."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_Q9fqyCpBselvrdnKXCS87Z","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"metis","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":600,"task":"Research D&D 2024 (the revised 2024 Player's Handbook) rules changes compared to 5e 2014. I need a comprehensive reference document for building a web app.\n\nFocus on:\n\n1. **Character Creation Changes:**\n   - New species/races list (2024 PHB) — what changed from 2014\n   - Class changes — all 12 classes, subclass timing, new features\n   - New background system (backgrounds now give feat + ability scores instead of races)\n   - Ability score generation rules\n   - New/changed feats\n\n2. **Combat & Mechanics Changes:**\n   - Weapon mastery system (new in 2024)\n   - Updated action economy (Influence, Search, Study actions)\n   - Spell changes — new/removed/modified spells\n   - Concentration rules changes\n   - Death save changes\n   - Exhaustion changes (new graduated system)\n\n3. **Spell List:**\n   - Full spell list organized by class and level (at least the spell names)\n   - New spells added in 2024\n   - Spells that were changed significantly\n\n4. **Classes Summary:**\n   - For each of the 12 classes: subclass options, key new features, spell progression if applicable\n\n5. **Species (Races) List:**\n   - All playable species in 2024 PHB with their traits\n\nOutput as a structured markdown document that a developer can reference when building a character sheet builder and rules engine. Be thorough — this will be the reference doc for the entire build."}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":688,"cacheRead":126745,"cacheWrite":423,"totalTokens":127859,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.0172,"cacheRead":0.0633725,"cacheWrite":0.0026437500000000003,"total":0.08323125}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774962012428}}
