{"type":"message","id":"1a081852","parentId":"52f14818","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:02:14.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nExactly. Itu advantage-nya dispatch model:\n\n- Kita tetap ngobrol soal apa aja — nggak ke-block nungguin task selesai\n- Agent kerja di background, selesai langsung lapor\n- Bisa dispatch multiple agent sekaligus (paralel)\n- Kamu nggak perlu monitor, gw yang relay hasilnya\n\nBasically kamu punya tim yang kerja di belakang layar, kamu tinggal terima hasilnya aja di chat ini. \n\nMetis masih riset D&D 2024 — begitu selesai gw kirim langsung."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":160,"cacheRead":128338,"cacheWrite":244,"totalTokens":128745,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004,"cacheRead":0.064169,"cacheWrite":0.001525,"total":0.06970900000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774962126090}}
