{"type":"message","id":"e86bf166","parentId":"f1fe22fc","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:12:07.804Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oke reference doc D&D 2024 udah gw compile. Ini ringkasan perubahan besar dari 2014 → 2024:\n\n**Perubahan Terbesar:**\n\n1. **Species gak kasih ability scores lagi** — sekarang dari Background\n2. **16 Background baru** — masing-masing kasih +2/+1 stat, 1 Origin Feat, skills, tool\n3. **Semua subclass di Level 3** (Cleric, Warlock, Sorcerer dulu di Lv1)\n4. **Weapon Mastery** — sistem baru, tiap senjata punya special effect (Cleave, Graze, Push, Vex, dll)\n5. **Divine Smite jadi spell** — Paladin gak bisa crit-fish lagi\n6. **Warlock jadi true caster** — spell slots normal, bukan short rest\n7. **Monk Ki → Focus Points**\n8. **Exhaustion** — simplified, -2 per level ke semua d20\n9. **Death saves persist** sampai long rest (gak reset waktu di-heal)\n10. **Two-Weapon Fighting** gak pake bonus action lagi\n\n**10 Species:** Aasimar, Dragonborn, Dwarf, Elf, Gnome, Goliath, Halfling, Human, Orc, Tiefling\n\n**12 Classes** dengan subclass timing yang seragam (semua Lv3)\n\nFull doc udah gw save. Mau gw kirim detail yang mana, atau langsung mulai build?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":401,"cacheRead":109092,"cacheWrite":4118,"totalTokens":113612,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.010025000000000001,"cacheRead":0.054546,"cacheWrite":0.0257375,"total":0.09031349999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774962717419}}
