{"type":"message","id":"a56d5988","parentId":"47236270","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:32:38.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBelum dimulai — tadi gw hold karena nunggu rules reference selesai dulu, dan itu udah done (gw compile sendiri karena Metis timeout).\n\nMau gw dispatch Uriel sekarang buat mulai build D&D web app? \n\n**MVP scope reminder:**\n1. PIN-based login (DM bikin room, kasih PIN ke player)\n2. Character Sheet Builder (2024 rules)\n3. Dice Roller (shared, real-time)\n4. Initiative Tracker\n5. Spell Book (2024)\n6. Desktop-first, responsive\n\nIni bakal lebih complex dari fitur-fitur tadi — probably perlu beberapa round. Mau gw gas sekarang?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":185,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":147866,"totalTokens":148054,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004625000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.9241625,"total":0.9288025}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774963945629}}
