{"type":"message","id":"a438814c","parentId":"7cd4bbac","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:45:24.871Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Backend works, HTML + CSS done, spells data done. Just missing `app.js` (the main JavaScript). Gw dispatch Uriel lagi buat finishin:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_joA20GgD1uMp66T42MBB6h","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"uriel","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":600,"task":"Finish the D&D 2024 Web App. The previous build timed out but got most things done. Here's what exists and what's missing:\n\n**EXISTS (don't touch these):**\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/server.js (353 lines, working — has API endpoints, WebSocket, PIN auth)\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/spells-data.js (spell data)\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/index.html (410 lines, complete HTML structure with all tabs)\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/styles.css (1212 lines, complete styling)\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/node_modules/ (dependencies installed)\n\n**MISSING — need to create:**\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js — THE MAIN JAVASCRIPT FILE\n\nRead the existing index.html and server.js first to understand the structure, IDs, and API endpoints. Then create app.js that wires everything together.\n\n**app.js needs to handle:**\n\n1. **Auth/Room System:**\n   - Create room (POST /api/rooms) → DM gets 6-digit PIN\n   - Join room (POST /api/rooms/join) with PIN\n   - Store room/player info in sessionStorage\n   - Show/hide DM-only controls based on role\n\n2. **Character Sheet:**\n   - Species/Class/Background dropdowns with D&D 2024 data\n   - Ability score methods: Standard Array (15,14,13,12,10,8), Point Buy (27 points), Manual\n   - Background bonuses (+2/+1 to ability scores)\n   - Auto-calculate: modifiers, HP, AC, proficiency bonus, saving throws, skill modifiers\n   - Save character (POST /api/characters), load character (GET /api/characters/:id)\n   - All 18 skills with proficiency checkboxes\n\n3. **Dice Roller:**\n   - Click dice buttons (d4,d6,d8,d10,d12,d20,d100)\n   - Multiple dice input (e.g. \"2d6+3\")\n   - Advantage/Disadvantage toggle for d20\n   - WebSocket: broadcast rolls to all players in room\n   - Roll history log with timestamps\n   - Simple roll animation (shake + reveal)\n\n4. **Initiative Tracker:**\n   - Add combatant (name, initiative roll, HP, AC)\n   - Auto-populate from party characters\n   - Sort by initiative (descending)\n   - \"Next Turn\" button (DM only) — cycles through combatants\n   - Highlight current turn\n   - HP adjustment (+/-)\n   - Conditions dropdown per combatant\n   - Remove combatant (DM only)\n\n5. **Spell Book:**\n   - Load spells from /api/spells endpoint\n   - Search by name\n   - Filter by level (0-9) and class\n   - Spell cards showing all details\n   - \"Prepare\" toggle per spell\n   - Spell slot tracker (checkboxes per level based on class/level)\n\n6. **Session Notes (DM):**\n   - Textarea for freeform notes\n   - Save notes (auto-save + manual save button)\n   - \"AI Summary\" button — POST to /api/session-summary with notes + recent dice rolls\n   - Display generated summaries\n   - Show AI summary button only for DM\n\n7. **WebSocket:**\n   - Connect to ws://host/dnd-ws (or wss:// if HTTPS)\n   - Events: dice_roll, initiative_update, turn_change, player_joined, player_left\n   - Reconnect on disconnect\n\n8. **Tab Navigation:**\n   - Match the tab buttons in index.html\n   - Show/hide tab content panels\n   - Remember last active tab\n\n**D&D 2024 Data to embed in app.js:**\n- Species traits (name, speed, darkvision, features)\n- Class data (hit die, saving throws, primary ability, armor/weapon proficiencies, spell progression)\n- Background data (skill profs, tool prof, ability score bonuses, feat)\n- Skill list with associated abilities\n- Basic feat list (origin feats)\n\n**ALSO DO:**\n- Register with pm2: pm2 start /home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/server.js --name dnd-app\n- pm2 save\n- Add Caddy routes (check if they exist first, add if missing):\n```\n@dnd path /dnd /dnd/*\nhandle @dnd {\n    uri strip_prefix /dnd\n    root * /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend\n    try_files {path} {path}/index.html /index.html\n    file_server\n    header Cache-Control \"no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate\"\n}\n\n@dndapi path /dnd-api /dnd-api/*\nhandle @dndapi {\n    uri strip_prefix /dnd-api\n    reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:3004\n}\n\n@dndws path /dnd-ws /dnd-ws/*\nhandle @dndws {\n    uri strip_prefix /dnd-ws\n    reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:3004\n}\n```\n- sudo systemctl reload caddy\n- Test that the app loads at /dnd and basic functions work"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":1445,"cacheRead":132085,"cacheWrite":756,"totalTokens":134287,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.036125000000000004,"cacheRead":0.06604249999999999,"cacheWrite":0.004725,"total":0.1068975}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774964697120}}
