{"type":"message","id":"c75f0562","parentId":"5809a8c3","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:54:18.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Actually, simplest fix — just have app.js call `/dnd-api/rooms` and have Caddy rewrite `/dnd-api/*` to `/api/*`:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_tudGzouaVhEHHhR6CCGMnO","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/caddy-dndapi-fix.txt << 'EOF'\n\t@dndapi path /dnd-api /dnd-api/*\n\thandle @dndapi {\n\t\turi replace /dnd-api /api 1\n\t\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:3004\n\t}\nEOF\n\n# Replace in Caddyfile\nsudo sed -i '/@dndapi/,/^[[:space:]]*}/c\\\\t@dndapi path /dnd-api /dnd-api/*\\n\\thandle @dndapi {\\n\\t\\turi replace /dnd-api /api 1\\n\\t\\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:3004\\n\\t}' /etc/caddy/Caddyfile\n\n# Verify\ngrep -A4 \"@dndapi\" /etc/caddy/Caddyfile"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":308,"cacheRead":163773,"cacheWrite":368,"totalTokens":164450,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0077,"cacheRead":0.0818865,"cacheWrite":0.0023,"total":0.0918915}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774965248688}}
