{"type":"message","id":"41d838d1","parentId":"44dac489","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:56:07.589Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_cvEMwuBzWIvIUWHkAWjtdw","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async function createRoom() {\n  const name = $('#dm-name').value.trim();\n  if (!name) return showError('Enter your name');\n  try {\n    const data = await api('/api/rooms', { method:'POST', body:{ dmName: name } });\n    state.roomPin = data.pin;\n    state.playerId = data.dmId;\n    state.playerName = data.dmName;\n    state.isDM = true;\n    saveSession();\n    enterApp();\n  } catch (e) { showError(e.message); }\n}\n\nasync function joinRoom() {\n  const pin = $('#room-pin').value.trim();\n  const name = $('#player-name').value.trim();\n  if (!pin || pin.length !== 6) return showError('Enter a valid 6-digit PIN');\n  if (!name) return showError('Enter your name');\n  try {\n    const data = await api(`/api/rooms/${pin}/join`, { method:'POST', body:{ playerName: name } });\n--\n  $('#create-room-btn').addEventListener('click', createRoom);\n  $('#join-room-btn').addEventListener('click', joinRoom);\n  $('#leave-room-btn').addEventListener('click', leaveRoom);\n\n  // Enter key handlers\n  $('#dm-name').addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter') createRoom(); });\n  $('#room-pin').addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter') $('#player-name').focus(); });\n  $('#player-name').addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter') joinRoom(); });\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// TAB NAV (MAIN APP)\n// ============================================================\n\nfunction initNavTabs() {\n  $$('.nav-btn').forEach(btn => {\n    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      switchTab(btn.dataset.tab);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"async function createRoom() {\n  const name = $('#dm-name').value.trim();\n  if (!name) return showError('Enter your name');\n  try {\n    const data = await api('/api/rooms', { method:'POST', body:{ dmName: name } });\n    state.roomPin = data.pin;\n    state.playerId = data.dmId;\n    state.playerName = data.dmName;\n    state.isDM = true;\n    saveSession();\n    enterApp();\n  } catch (e) { showError(e.message); }\n}\n\nasync function joinRoom() {\n  const pin = $('#room-pin').value.trim();\n  const name = $('#player-name').value.trim();\n  if (!pin || pin.length !== 6) return showError('Enter a valid 6-digit PIN');\n  if (!name) return showError('Enter your name');\n  try {\n    const data = await api(`/api/rooms/${pin}/join`, { method:'POST', body:{ playerName: name } });\n--\n  $('#create-room-btn').addEventListener('click', createRoom);\n  $('#join-room-btn').addEventListener('click', joinRoom);\n  $('#leave-room-btn').addEventListener('click', leaveRoom);\n\n  // Enter key handlers\n  $('#dm-name').addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter') createRoom(); });\n  $('#room-pin').addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter') $('#player-name').focus(); });\n  $('#player-name').addEventListener('keydown', e => { if (e.key === 'Enter') joinRoom(); });\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// TAB NAV (MAIN APP)\n// ============================================================\n\nfunction initNavTabs() {\n  $$('.nav-btn').forEach(btn => {\n    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      switchTab(btn.dataset.tab);","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774965367583}}
{"type":"message","id":"353e65bb","parentId":"41d838d1","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:56:12.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue — `api('/api/rooms', ...)` but the API is at `/dnd-api/rooms` through Caddy. Let me check the api function:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_xd48zt83zYhB9BqgVlOtVD","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -B2 -A15 \"^async function api\\|^function api\\|const api\\|const API\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js | head -25"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":137,"cacheRead":166976,"cacheWrite":602,"totalTokens":167716,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.003425,"cacheRead":0.08348799999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0037625000000000002,"total":0.0906805}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774965367590}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d1ae431","parentId":"353e65bb","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:56:12.975Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_xd48zt83zYhB9BqgVlOtVD","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// ---- API base (works behind Caddy reverse proxy or direct) ----\nconst API = (() => {\n  const loc = window.location;\n  // If served from /dnd, API is at /dnd-api\n  if (loc.pathname.startsWith('/dnd')) return '/dnd-api';\n  // Fallback: same origin, port 3004\n  return `${loc.protocol}//${loc.hostname}:3004`;\n})();\n\nconst WS_URL = (() => {\n  const loc = window.location;\n  const proto = loc.protocol === 'https:' ? 'wss:' : 'ws:';\n  if (loc.pathname.startsWith('/dnd')) return `${proto}//${loc.host}/dnd-ws`;\n  return `${proto}//${loc.hostname}:3004`;\n})();\n\n// ============================================================\n--\nfunction profBonus(level) { return Math.ceil(level / 4) + 1; }\n\nasync function api(path, opts = {}) {\n  const url = `${API}${path}`;\n  const res = await fetch(url, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', ...opts.headers },"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":17,"aggregated":"// ---- API base (works behind Caddy reverse proxy or direct) ----\nconst API = (() => {\n  const loc = window.location;\n  // If served from /dnd, API is at /dnd-api\n  if (loc.pathname.startsWith('/dnd')) return '/dnd-api';\n  // Fallback: same origin, port 3004\n  return `${loc.protocol}//${loc.hostname}:3004`;\n})();\n\nconst WS_URL = (() => {\n  const loc = window.location;\n  const proto = loc.protocol === 'https:' ? 'wss:' : 'ws:';\n  if (loc.pathname.startsWith('/dnd')) return `${proto}//${loc.host}/dnd-ws`;\n  return `${proto}//${loc.hostname}:3004`;\n})();\n\n// ============================================================\n--\nfunction profBonus(level) { return Math.ceil(level / 4) + 1; }\n\nasync function api(path, opts = {}) {\n  const url = `${API}${path}`;\n  const res = await fetch(url, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', ...opts.headers },","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774965372969}}
{"type":"message","id":"fde3e272","parentId":"5d1ae431","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:56:23.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So `API = '/dnd-api'` and then `api('/api/rooms')` makes the URL `/dnd-api/api/rooms` — double `/api`! The function calls should use just `/rooms` not `/api/rooms`."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_NK18O6C6Ua5pKeSlOCEmrl","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Fix all api() calls — remove the /api prefix since API base already handles routing\nsed -i \"s|api('/api/|api('/|g\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js\nsed -i \"s|api(\\\"/api/|api(\\\"/|g\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js\nsed -i \"s|api(\\`/api/|api(\\`/|g\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js\n\n# But Caddy rewrites /dnd-api → /api, so the final URL to server should be /api/rooms\n# Currently: API='/dnd-api', path='/rooms' → URL='/dnd-api/rooms' → Caddy rewrites to '/api/rooms' → server has '/api/rooms' ✅\n# Wait, Caddy does: uri replace /dnd-api /api 1\n# So /dnd-api/rooms → /api/rooms ✅ That should work!\n\n# Verify\ngrep \"api('\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js | head -10\necho \"---\"\n# Test full chain\ncurl -s https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd-api/rooms -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"dmName\":\"Test\"}' 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":445,"cacheRead":167578,"cacheWrite":442,"totalTokens":168466,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.011125000000000001,"cacheRead":0.083789,"cacheWrite":0.0027625,"total":0.0976815}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774965372978}}
