{"type":"message","id":"3f06a20e","parentId":"59f3ad5f","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:57:34.203Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ACF04AAF411A21DB1157E784ECC373FB\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nHmmm, jadi GM yang buat char nya?"}],"timestamp":1774965454192}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd0aadd8","parentId":"3f06a20e","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:57:43.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNah itu emang perlu dibenerin. Sekarang flow-nya:\n\n1. DM create room → dapet PIN\n2. Player join pake PIN\n3. **Tapi character sheet cuma ada satu shared** — harusnya tiap player bikin char masing-masing\n\nYang bener harusnya:\n- DM create room → share PIN\n- Player join → langsung bisa bikin/edit character sendiri\n- DM bisa lihat semua character party\n- DM nggak perlu bikin character (kecuali NPC)\n\nMau gw dispatch Uriel buat fix flow-nya? Sekalian gw list perbaikan:\n\n1. **Tiap player punya character sheet sendiri** (linked ke player ID)\n2. **DM punya \"Party View\"** — lihat semua character sekaligus\n3. **DM bisa bikin NPC/monster stat blocks** terpisah\n4. **Player cuma bisa edit character sendiri**\n\nGas fix?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":251,"cacheRead":169266,"cacheWrite":346,"totalTokens":169866,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.006275,"cacheRead":0.084633,"cacheWrite":0.0021625,"total":0.0930855}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774965454199}}
{"type":"message","id":"5951bb99","parentId":"dd0aadd8","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:57:44.766Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ACE5CC9EDF950A37D55CEB41FC4AE573\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nbukannya gm yang monitoring"}],"timestamp":1774965464753}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a0818f6","parentId":"5951bb99","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:58:09.723Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBetul! GM itu monitor, bukan bikin character. Flow yang bener:\n\n- **Player** → bikin & manage character sendiri\n- **GM/DM** → monitor semua player, manage initiative, NPCs/monsters, session notes, AI summary\n\nJadi GM dashboard-nya beda dari player view. Gw fix:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_x6yoZKi3PDBr4rzimmTnCd","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"uriel","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":600,"task":"Fix the D&D web app (Paul Simulator) role-based flow. Currently the character sheet is shared — needs to be per-player, with DM as a monitor/controller only.\n\n**Files to modify:**\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js (main JS, ~1800 lines)\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/index.html (410 lines)\n- /home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/server.js (353 lines)\n\nRead these files first to understand current structure.\n\n**Current problem:** DM and players see the same character sheet. DM shouldn't create characters — DM monitors and controls.\n\n**Fix the flow to:**\n\n### Player Flow:\n1. Join room with PIN + name\n2. See their OWN character sheet — create/edit their character\n3. Can use: Character Sheet (own), Dice Roller, Spell Book, Spell Slot Tracker\n4. Can see Initiative Tracker (but can't control Next Turn)\n5. Cannot see Session Notes tab\n\n### DM/GM Flow:\n1. Create room → get PIN to share\n2. **Party Overview tab** (replaces Character Sheet for DM):\n   - See ALL player characters in a compact card grid\n   - Each card shows: player name, species, class, level, HP, AC, key stats\n   - Click to expand/view full character details (read-only)\n   - Real-time updates when players edit their characters\n3. **Initiative Tracker** — full control (add combatants, Next Turn, HP adjust, conditions, add monsters/NPCs)\n4. **Session Notes** — write notes, AI Summary button\n5. **Dice Roller** — same as players\n6. **NPC/Monster Quick Add** in initiative — name, HP, AC, initiative (no full character sheet needed for monsters)\n\n### Backend Changes:\n- Characters should be linked to a player ID AND room PIN\n- GET /api/rooms/:pin/characters → list all characters in room (for DM party view)\n- Each character has an `ownerId` field matching the player ID\n- Players can only edit their own character\n- WebSocket: broadcast character updates so DM sees changes in real-time (event: 'character_update')\n\n### Frontend Changes (index.html):\n- Add a \"Party Overview\" section/tab that only DM sees\n- Hide \"Character Sheet\" create/edit for DM (or show read-only)\n- Hide \"Session Notes\" tab for players\n- Show/hide based on state.isDM\n\n### Frontend Changes (app.js):\n- On enterApp(): check if DM → show DM tabs, hide player-only tabs\n- Character sheet: load player's own character by ownerId\n- Party overview: fetch all room characters, render as compact cards\n- WebSocket: listen for character_update events to refresh party view\n- Initiative: auto-populate from room characters (not just local)\n\n**IMPORTANT:**\n- Don't break existing functionality\n- Keep all the existing D&D 2024 data (species, classes, backgrounds, spells)\n- Keep the dark fantasy styling\n- Test that both DM and Player flows work\n- pm2 restart dnd-app when done"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":935,"cacheRead":169612,"cacheWrite":433,"totalTokens":170983,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.023375,"cacheRead":0.08480599999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0027062500000000003,"total":0.11090224999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774965464760}}
