{"type":"message","id":"3d5dc74e","parentId":"4ba66066","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:00:10.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ini flow lengkapnya, bisa dilihat visual di browser:\n\nhttps://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd/flow.html\n\n**Ringkasan flow:**\n\n**DM/GM:**\n- Create room → dapet PIN → share ke players\n- Lihat *Party Overview* (semua character cards, real-time)\n- Control initiative (add monsters, Next Turn, HP, conditions)\n- Session Notes + AI Summary\n- Dice Roller\n\n**Player:**\n- Join room pake PIN\n- Bikin & edit character sendiri (cuma bisa edit punya sendiri)\n- Spell Book + slot tracker\n- Dice Roller\n- Lihat initiative (tapi gak bisa control)\n\n**Real-time sync:**\n- Dice rolls → semua orang lihat\n- Character edits → DM party overview auto-update\n- Initiative → broadcast ke semua\n\nCek flow page-nya dulu, kalau udah oke baru gw dispatch Uriel buat implement sesuai flow ini. Ada yang mau diubah/tambah?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":262,"cacheRead":187671,"cacheWrite":100,"totalTokens":188034,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00655,"cacheRead":0.0938355,"cacheWrite":0.000625,"total":0.10101550000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774965600719}}
