{"type":"message","id":"d68a0048","parentId":"d0900055","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:05:49.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🔥 **Dispatched Uriel** → upgrading dice roller\n\nYang bakal ada:\n- **3D dice animation** — tumble/spin/bounce, tiap dice type beda bentuk & warna\n- **7 dice types**: d4 (merah), d6 (biru), d8 (hijau), d10 (ungu), d12 (orange), d20 (gold), d100 (silver)\n- **Nat 20 = CRITICAL!** (gold glow) / **Nat 1 = FUMBLE!** (red glow)\n- **Multiple dice**: 2d6, 3d6, 4d6 drop lowest\n- **Quick roll presets**: Attack, Damage, Ability Check, Saving Throw\n- **Dice tray** visual area\n- **Sound effects** (toggle on/off)\n- Advantage/Disadvantage + custom modifiers\n\nTunggu ya ~5-10 min."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":233,"cacheRead":192174,"cacheWrite":1384,"totalTokens":193792,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005825,"cacheRead":0.09608699999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00865,"total":0.110567}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774965940353}}
