{"type":"message","id":"e3e99974","parentId":"eb461348","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:07:46.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood point. Jadi kamu mau:\n\n1. **Session persistence** — data room, characters, notes nggak hilang walau server restart atau browser ditutup\n2. **Save ke Obsidian** — session history/summaries sync ke Obsidian vault biar bisa dibaca kapan aja\n\nSekarang data disimpan di JSON files (`/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/`) yang harusnya persistent. Tapi kalau browser di-close, session state ilang karena pake `sessionStorage`.\n\nYang perlu di-fix:\n- **Browser side**: Ganti `sessionStorage` → `localStorage` biar PIN login persist walau browser ditutup\n- **Server side**: Data udah persistent di JSON files, tapi perlu auto-backup\n- **Obsidian sync**: Setelah tiap session (atau manual), save summary + session data ke Obsidian vault\n\nGw tambahin ini ke task list buat Uriel/Rafael yang lagi jalan. Kalau mereka timeout, gw dispatch lagi khusus buat ini.\n\nObsidian vault kamu di: `/home/openclaw/livesync-bridge/vault/` kan? Nanti session summaries masuk ke folder `D&D Sessions/` di vault itu."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":313,"cacheRead":25861,"cacheWrite":174313,"totalTokens":200490,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.007825,"cacheRead":0.0129305,"cacheWrite":1.08945625,"total":1.11022675}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774966055316}}
{"type":"message","id":"25584c3b","parentId":"e3e99974","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:07:46.883Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good point. Jadi kamu mau:\n\n1. **Session persistence** — data room, characters, notes nggak hilang walau server restart atau browser ditutup\n2. **Save ke Obsidian** — session history/summaries sync ke Obsidian vault biar bisa dibaca kapan aja\n\nSekarang data disimpan di JSON files (`/home/openclaw/dnd-app/data/`) yang harusnya persistent. Tapi kalau browser di-close, session state ilang karena pake `sessionStorage`.\n\nYang perlu di-fix:\n- **Browser side**: Ganti `sessionStorage` → `localStorage` biar PIN login persist walau browser ditutup\n- **Server side**: Data udah persistent di JSON files, tapi perlu auto-backup\n- **Obsidian sync**: Setelah tiap session (atau manual), save summary + session data ke Obsidian vault\n\nGw tambahin ini ke task list buat Uriel/Rafael yang lagi jalan. Kalau mereka timeout, gw dispatch lagi khusus buat ini.\n\nObsidian vault kamu di: `/home/openclaw/livesync-bridge/vault/` kan? Nanti session summaries masuk ke folder `D&D Sessions/` di vault itu."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774966066853}}
