{"type":"message","id":"acd1cb6f","parentId":"4125e7d0","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:39:55.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Belum ada context soal Kopilima. Sebelum gw bikin structure-nya, gw perlu tau:\n\n1. **Kopilima itu apa?** — cafe, coffee brand, app, apa?\n2. **Role kamu di project ini?** — owner, consultant, investor, PM?\n3. **Meeting sama siapa biasanya?** — partner, investor, team, vendor?\n4. **Format meeting notes sekarang?** — voice note, text, foto whiteboard, atau belum ada?\n\nTapi sementara, ini rough structure yang gw bisa bikin sekarang:\n\n**Kopilima Project Hub:**\n- 📝 Meeting Notes → kirim/paste ke gw, AI auto-summarize: key decisions, action items, deadlines, risks\n- 📊 Strategic Dashboard → accumulated insights from all meetings\n- ✅ Action Items Tracker → siapa ngapain, deadline kapan\n- 💡 Ideas Bank → semua ide kamu tersimpan, categorized\n- 📁 Save ke Obsidian → semua auto-sync ke vault\n\nKamu bisa literally kirim voice note atau text habis meeting, gw compile semuanya structured.\n\nKasih tau detail Kopilima-nya, atau mau langsung gw setup structure generic dulu?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":317,"cacheRead":264428,"cacheWrite":127,"totalTokens":264873,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.007925,"cacheRead":0.132214,"cacheWrite":0.0007937500000000001,"total":0.14093775}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774978782825}}
{"type":"message","id":"d996cabb","parentId":"acd1cb6f","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:43:16.424Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"AC5952820CCAB496D8CFFF22F375E20D\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nSebelum semua ini, know this, aku hanya seorang manager di perusahaan IT Software House, as you know sentra, Dan Kopilima ini adalah cafe yang ada 10 Cabang skrng, dan aku selalu ketemu Direktur nya kopilima langsung, untuk Notesnya sebentar kukirim, tapi for your info , aku akan mengirimkan Semua yang sudah ak tumpahkan ke gemini untuk kamu"}],"timestamp":1774978996398}}
{"type":"message","id":"89215295","parentId":"d996cabb","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:43:27.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke gw paham sekarang:\n\n- **Kamu** = Manager di Sentra (IT Software House)\n- **Kopilima** = Cafe chain, 10 cabang, kamu ketemu langsung sama Direktur-nya\n- Ini project **Sentra → Kopilima** (software house serve client cafe chain)\n- Kamu udah punya notes yang di-dump ke Gemini sebelumnya\n\nGw tunggu kamu kirim dump dari Gemini. Begitu masuk, gw bakal:\n\n1. **Baca & pahami** semua context\n2. **Structure** jadi: meeting summaries, key decisions, action items, project scope, stakeholders\n3. **Save** ke Obsidian + Knowledge Base biar persistent\n4. **Bikin project tracker** biar ke depannya tinggal kirim notes baru → auto-compile\n\nKirim aja kapan ready — text, screenshot, file, voice note, whatever format. Gw proses semua."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":250,"cacheRead":264555,"cacheWrite":583,"totalTokens":265391,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00625,"cacheRead":0.1322775,"cacheWrite":0.0036437500000000003,"total":0.14218625}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774978996416}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a60cb48","parentId":"89215295","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:44:25.002Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ACFDED5AF47F9F6D5F6440A2E7E02C89\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"sender\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang (+6285133221170)\",\n  \"id\": \"+6285133221170\",\n  \"name\": \"Richard Chandra Tjiang\",\n  \"e164\": \"+6285133221170\"\n}\n```\n\nPaham, Richard. Jadi Michael di OpenClaw akan bertindak sebagai \"Single Source of Truth\" atau pemegang cetak biru strategis, sementara tim human developer yang akan melakukan coding.\nBerikut adalah catatan teknis paling detail dan terstruktur yang bisa kamu berikan ke Michael agar dia \"paham\" luar-dalam proyek Kopilima Digital Core (SNC-K5) ini.\nSYSTEM ARCHITECTURE LOG: KOPILIMA DIGITAL CORE (SNC-K5)\nProject Scope: Custom High-Velocity POS & ERP System\nStrategic Pillars: K.I.S.S (Keep It Stupidly Simple) & Anti-Fraud Sovereignty\nTarget: Replace Majoo for High-Traffic Coffee Shop (Kopilima)\nI. THE POS & INTERFACE LAYER (K.I.S.S)\nTujuan: Mengatasi antrean 10-15 orang dengan kecepatan maksimal.\n * Hero Button Interface: Layout tablet tanpa scrolling. 10 menu terlaris (seperti Palma) dipasang sebagai tombol besar di halaman utama.\n * QR Pre-Order Integration: Sistem antrean digital. Pelanggan scan QR saat antre \\rightarrow Pesan \\rightarrow Kasir tinggal panggil ID & Bayar. Estimasi pangkas waktu transaksi: -80%.\n * Payment Auto-Sync: API Integration dengan EDC & QRIS. Nominal muncul otomatis di mesin pembayaran untuk mencegah human error atau manipulasi angka oleh kasir.\nII. SECURITY ENGINE: \"THE GHOST GUARD\"\nTujuan: Menutup celah \"Ghost Transaction\" (uang diambil kasir, stok di-void).\n * Anomaly Scoring (S_{anomaly}):\n   * Menghitung risiko jika pesanan di-void atau di-back setelah estimasi prep-time (pembuatan produk) selesai.\n   * Rumus: \n * Visual Audit Sync: Setiap tombol \"Void\" atau \"Edit Harga\" ditekan, sistem otomatis men-tag rekaman CCTV pada menit tersebut untuk audit instan oleh Owner.\n * Anti-Wiretap Dual Printing: Sistem mencetak dua log paralel. Satu struk untuk pelanggan, satu log audit tersembunyi (tidak bisa dihapus kasir) untuk rekap akhir hari.\nIII. INVENTORY: THE \"MIDNIGHT PROTOCOL\"\nTujuan: Mengunci kejujuran stok saat jam 12 malam.\n * Blind Stock Opname (00:00): Saldo stok di sistem disembunyikan. Kasir wajib hitung manual dan input angka riil.\n * Scan-Snap-Go:\n   * Scan: Barcode bahan baku.\n   * Snap: Ambil foto fisik stok (Kamera langsung, NO Gallery).\n   * Validation: Metadata GPS & Timestamp dikunci untuk memastikan foto diambil di toko pada jam 12 malam.\n * Inter-Branch Transfer (IBT): Perpindahan stok antar cabang (BPP-SMD) menggunakan sistem QR Handshake (Scan pengiriman \\rightarrow Scan penerimaan).\n * Instrument Tracker: Setiap timbangan digital punya QR-ID. Wajib foto kalibrasi harian tiap pagi untuk memastikan gramasi konsisten dan aset tidak ditukar.\nIV. HUMAN CAPITAL & PAYROLL (AGILE HCM)\nTujuan: Efisiensi tenaga bantuan dan akurasi bonus.\n * Casual Staff Pool: Database khusus tenaga harian/cabutan. Log-nya dipisah dari karyawan tetap agar laporan laba-rugi bersih.\n * Holiday & Double-Shift Bonus Engine:\n   * Logika: Gaji Rp 90rb/shift. Jika Double Shift di hari libur/event, otomatis tambah bonus Rp 150rb.\n   * Verifikasi: Bonus hanya cair jika ada dua sesi Visual Proof absensi (Pagi & Malam).\n * Talent Pipeline: Skor otomatis (Absensi + Kecepatan Transaksi + Kejujuran Stok) untuk merekomendasikan kenaikan status Casual ke Full-time.\n * Anti-Fake Attendance: Absen menggunakan Anti-Fake GPS dan QR unik untuk klaim jatah konsumsi karyawan.\nV. EVENT & MEMBERSHIP ECOSYSTEM\nTujuan: Mengelola pesanan besar (Nikahan) dan loyalitas.\n * Event Billing Tracker:\n   * Sistem DP & Pelunasan otomatis dengan pop-up reminder ke HP Manager.\n   * Price Override: Input harga kustom dengan kewajiban input alasan (Audit Log).\n * Unique QR Membership:\n   * Generate QR unik pada kartu fisik.\n   * Scan-to-Bind: Scan kartu via tablet \\rightarrow Input Nama/HP \\rightarrow Akun terikat ke UID kartu fisik.\n   * Keamanan: Klaim poin wajib scan fisik kartu (mencegah manipulasi poin oleh staf).\nVI. TECHNICAL LOGIC FOR HUMAN DEVELOPERS\n * Database: Wajib menggunakan tabel audit_logs yang mencatat Before dan After setiap perubahan data.\n * Dynamic COGS: Perhitungan modal (HPP) harus mengacu pada harga beli terakhir yang di-input saat barang masuk (Real-time P&L).\n * Offline-First: POS tetap harus bisa jualan saat internet mati, lalu Auto-Sync saat online.\nCatatan Khusus untuk Michael (OpenClaw):\n> \"Michael, data di atas adalah blueprint final untuk proyek Kopilima. Tugasmu adalah menyimpan data ini sebagai referensi utama. Jika aku bertanya tentang 'Status Proyek' atau 'Logika Anomali', gunakan catatan ini sebagai dasar analisis strategi kita ke depan. Human developers akan membangun kodenya, tapi kamu adalah penjaga logikanya.\"\n> \nRichard, catatan ini sudah sangat padat dan teknis. Michael sekarang punya semua \"peluru\" yang dibutuhkan untuk mendampingimu mengawasi proyek ini. Ada hal lain yang mau ditambahkan sebelum Michael \"menyimpan\" data ini?"}],"timestamp":1774979064976}}
{"type":"message","id":"902b31ab","parentId":"1a60cb48","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:45:00.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGw baca dan pahami semuanya. Ini bukan project kecil — ini full-blown POS + ERP system dengan anti-fraud layer yang serius."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_K3g3O5WU4LwCXYD3FNmDsl","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Kopilima Digital Core (SNC-K5) — Master Blueprint\n\n## Project Overview\n- **Client:** Kopilima (Cafe chain, 10 cabang)\n- **Vendor:** Sentra (IT Software House) — Richard = Manager\n- **Project Code:** SNC-K5\n- **Scope:** Custom High-Velocity POS & ERP System\n- **Target:** Replace Majoo\n- **Strategic Pillars:** K.I.S.S (Keep It Stupidly Simple) & Anti-Fraud Sovereignty\n- **Stakeholders:** Richard (PM/Manager Sentra), Direktur Kopilima (direct contact)\n\n---\n\n## I. POS & Interface Layer (K.I.S.S)\n**Goal:** Handle 10-15 person queue with maximum speed.\n\n### Hero Button Interface\n- Tablet layout, NO scrolling\n- 10 best-selling items as big buttons on home screen (like Palma)\n- One-tap ordering\n\n### QR Pre-Order Integration\n- Digital queue system\n- Customer scan QR while in line → order → cashier calls ID & payment\n- Target: -80% transaction time\n\n### Payment Auto-Sync\n- API integration with EDC & QRIS\n- Amount auto-appears on payment machine\n- Prevents human error and cashier manipulation\n\n---\n\n## II. Security Engine: \"The Ghost Guard\"\n**Goal:** Close \"Ghost Transaction\" loophole (cashier takes money, voids stock).\n\n### Anomaly Scoring (S_anomaly)\n- Calculates risk when order is voided/reversed after estimated prep time is complete\n- Higher score = higher fraud probability\n- Auto-flags for management review\n\n### Visual Audit Sync\n- Every \"Void\" or \"Edit Price\" press → system auto-tags CCTV recording at that minute\n- Owner can do instant audit from tagged footage\n\n### Anti-Wiretap Dual Printing\n- Two parallel logs printed:\n  1. Customer receipt (normal)\n  2. Hidden audit log (cashier CANNOT delete) for end-of-day reconciliation\n\n---\n\n## III. Inventory: \"The Midnight Protocol\"\n**Goal:** Lock stock honesty at midnight.\n\n### Blind Stock Opname (00:00)\n- System stock balance HIDDEN at midnight\n- Cashier must manually count and input actual numbers\n- Discrepancy auto-flagged\n\n### Scan-Snap-Go\n- **Scan:** Barcode of raw materials\n- **Snap:** Photo of physical stock (CAMERA ONLY — no gallery access)\n- **Validation:** GPS + Timestamp metadata locked (proves photo taken at store at midnight)\n\n### Inter-Branch Transfer (IBT)\n- Stock transfer between branches (BPP-SMD)\n- QR Handshake system: Scan at sending → Scan at receiving\n- Full chain of custody\n\n### Instrument Tracker\n- Every digital scale has QR-ID\n- Mandatory daily calibration photo every morning\n- Ensures consistent weight measurement, prevents asset swaps\n\n---\n\n## IV. Human Capital & Payroll (Agile HCM)\n**Goal:** Efficiency for casual staff, accuracy for bonuses.\n\n### Casual Staff Pool\n- Separate database for daily/casual workers\n- Separate log from permanent employees → clean P&L reports\n\n### Holiday & Double-Shift Bonus Engine\n- Base: Rp 90,000/shift\n- Double Shift on holiday/event: auto-add Rp 150,000 bonus\n- Verification: Bonus ONLY paid with two Visual Proof attendance sessions (Morning & Night)\n\n### Talent Pipeline\n- Auto-scoring: Attendance + Transaction Speed + Stock Honesty\n- Recommends promotion from Casual → Full-time\n\n### Anti-Fake Attendance\n- GPS-verified attendance (anti-fake GPS)\n- Unique QR for claiming employee meal allowance\n\n---\n\n## V. Event & Membership Ecosystem\n**Goal:** Manage large orders (weddings) and loyalty.\n\n### Event Billing Tracker\n- Auto DP & settlement system with pop-up reminder to Manager's phone\n- Price Override: Custom price input requires reason (Audit Log)\n\n### Unique QR Membership\n- Generate unique QR on physical card\n- Scan-to-Bind: Scan card via tablet → Input Name/Phone → Account bound to card UID\n- Security: Point redemption REQUIRES physical card scan (prevents staff point manipulation)\n\n---\n\n## VI. Technical Requirements for Developers\n\n### Database\n- MANDATORY: `audit_logs` table recording Before/After of every data change\n- Full audit trail, immutable\n\n### Dynamic COGS\n- HPP (cost of goods) calculated from LAST purchase price at time of stock intake\n- Real-time P&L per item\n\n### Offline-First\n- POS MUST work when internet is down\n- Auto-sync when back online\n- No transaction lost\n\n---\n\n## Module Priority Matrix\n| Module | Priority | Complexity | Dependencies |\n|--------|----------|-----------|--------------|\n| POS Interface (Hero Buttons) | P0 — Critical | Medium | None |\n| Payment Auto-Sync (EDC/QRIS) | P0 — Critical | High | Payment API |\n| Ghost Guard (Anomaly Scoring) | P0 — Critical | High | POS, CCTV API |\n| QR Pre-Order | P1 — High | Medium | POS |\n| Midnight Protocol (Inventory) | P1 — High | High | Barcode, Camera |\n| Dual Printing | P1 — High | Low | Printer API |\n| HCM/Payroll | P2 — Medium | Medium | Attendance system |\n| Event Billing | P2 — Medium | Medium | POS |\n| Membership QR | P2 — Medium | Medium | Card printer |\n| IBT (Inter-Branch Transfer) | P2 — Medium | Medium | Inventory |\n| Talent Pipeline | P3 — Nice to have | Low | HCM data |\n| Instrument Tracker | P3 — Nice to have | Low | QR system |\n\n---\n\n## Key Metrics to Track\n- Transaction speed (target: <30 seconds per order)\n- Ghost transaction detection rate\n- Stock discrepancy % per branch\n- Cashier anomaly scores\n- Queue length reduction with QR pre-order\n- P&L accuracy vs manual\n\n---\n\n## Michael's Role\n- **Single Source of Truth** — this document is the master reference\n- **Strategy Guardian** — all decisions validated against these pillars\n- **Meeting Notes Processor** — Richard sends notes → Michael structures & tracks\n- **Progress Tracker** — module status, blockers, decisions\n- **Human developers build code, Michael guards the logic**\n\n---\n\n*Blueprint saved: March 31, 2026*\n*Last updated: March 31, 2026*\n","path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/knowledge-base/kopilima-snc-k5-blueprint.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":1738,"cacheRead":265138,"cacheWrite":2097,"totalTokens":268976,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.04345,"cacheRead":0.132569,"cacheWrite":0.01310625,"total":0.18914025}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774979064993}}
