{"type":"message","id":"e3b44990","parentId":"70f9a8f9","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:59:44.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tersimpan ✅\n\nBeberapa hal baru yang gw tangkep dari dump ini yang nggak ada di blueprint sebelumnya:\n\n**Tambahan penting:**\n- **Shift kosong alert** — kalau shift malam biasa 5 orang tapi cuma 3 yang isi, system harus alert\n- **Referral System** — karyawan bisa ajak teman buat isi posisi casual, potensi naik full-time\n- **Surat Peringatan (SP)** — fitur admin HR\n- **Minimum Purchase per event** — bukan cuma custom pricing\n- **Pop-up reminder ke HP Manager** — buat persiapan event, jadwal pelunasan\n\nSekarang gw punya 2 dokumen Kopilima:\n1. **Blueprint** (arsitektur & logic)\n2. **Operational Notes** (detail lapangan & workflow)\n\nDua-duanya di Knowledge Base + Obsidian vault.\n\nMasih ada dump lagi dari Gemini, atau ini udah semua? Kalau udah complete, gw bisa bikin **project tracker** biar tiap meeting notes baru tinggal kirim → auto-process."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":297,"cacheRead":272725,"cacheWrite":426,"totalTokens":273449,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.007425,"cacheRead":0.1363625,"cacheWrite":0.0026625,"total":0.146455}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774979973767}}
