{"type":"message","id":"72f660da","parentId":"b625c5f2","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:00:15.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hmm, gw belum detect grup baru. WhatsApp group policy kita `\"groupPolicy\": \"open\"` jadi harusnya gw bisa terima.\n\nGrup apa? Kopilima project group? Gw belum lihat pesan masuk dari grup baru — mungkin belum ada yang chat di situ, atau gw perlu waktu buat sync.\n\nCoba kirim pesan di grup itu, nanti gw lihat apakah masuk."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":121,"cacheRead":273618,"cacheWrite":131,"totalTokens":273871,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0030250000000000003,"cacheRead":0.136809,"cacheWrite":0.00081875,"total":0.14065775}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980007126}}
