{"type":"message","id":"fe02327b","parentId":"84b97b27","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:03:19.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGw belum lihat tag/mention dari grup baru masuk ke sini. Kemungkinan:\n\n1. Nomor gateway (+6281938953639) belum di-add ke grup\n2. Atau udah di-add tapi gw belum nerima pesan karena WhatsApp gateway lagi reconnect-reconnect terus (kamu lihat tadi disconnect/connect loop)\n\nCoba cek — yang kamu add ke grup itu nomor **+6281938953639** kan? Itu nomor WhatsApp gateway gw.\n\nKalau udah bener, coba tag lagi atau kirim pesan langsung di grup — begitu masuk, gw bakal respond."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":173,"cacheRead":273749,"cacheWrite":279,"totalTokens":274204,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004325,"cacheRead":0.13687449999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00174375,"total":0.14295824999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980187350}}
