{"type":"message","id":"ed8fb0db","parentId":"3c342b10","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:04:09.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOke gw tunggu. Kalau ada pesan dari grup masuk, gw bakal respond langsung.\n\nBtw nanti di grup Kopilima, gw harus behave gimana? Beberapa opsi:\n\n1. **Silent observer** — cuma dengerin, nggak reply kecuali di-tag. Semua notes gw process di background.\n2. **Active participant** — respond kalau ada pertanyaan teknis, kasih input strategi\n3. **Secretary mode** — setiap meeting/diskusi selesai, gw auto-summarize dan kirim recap ke kamu (DM, bukan di grup)\n\nMau yang mana? Atau kombinasi?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":173,"cacheRead":274028,"cacheWrite":332,"totalTokens":274536,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.004325,"cacheRead":0.137014,"cacheWrite":0.002075,"total":0.143429}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980241744}}
