{"type":"message","id":"65be2483","parentId":"600d5c88","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:05:41.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOh grup Sentra — kantor kamu! Oke beda context.\n\nDi grup Sentra gw harus lebih hati-hati — ini rekan kerja/tim kamu. Mau gw behave gimana di situ?\n\n1. **Diem kecuali di-tag** — paling aman, nggak bikin awkward sama tim\n2. **Respond kalau di-tag** — jawab pertanyaan, bantu teknis\n3. **Full assistant mode** — kayak di sini\n\nGw recommend opsi 2 — respond kalau di-tag aja. Di grup kantor nggak mau terlalu noisy.\n\nDan yang penting — gw nggak bakal share info personal kamu (DataFlow, D&D, contact list, dll) di grup. Strictly professional.\n\nMau gimana?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":211,"cacheRead":274360,"cacheWrite":339,"totalTokens":274913,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.005275,"cacheRead":0.13718,"cacheWrite":0.00211875,"total":0.14458875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980332374}}
