{"type":"message","id":"2b9c21e8","parentId":"e1046598","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:08:35.543Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oke gw paham sekarang. Group policy udah `open` tapi kayaknya default behavior di grup WhatsApp itu **mention-only** — gw cuma respond kalau di-tag. Dan mungkin tag-nya nggak ke-detect.\n\nCoba di grup Sentra, tag gw pake **nomor** bukan nama. Atau kirim pesan yang isi `@6281938953639`. \n\nAtau mau gw check — nama grup Sentra apa? Gw bisa coba cari di WhatsApp session:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_rcUFMd3NYiD50jpNJIwztX","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["group"],"activeMinutes":60,"messageLimit":3}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":229,"cacheRead":279560,"cacheWrite":326,"totalTokens":280116,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005725,"cacheRead":0.13978,"cacheWrite":0.0020375000000000002,"total":0.1475475}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774980506187}}
