{"type":"message","id":"e6149b6d","parentId":"47707d8f","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:13:17.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"WhatsApp linked dan OK. Tapi grup messages nggak masuk.\n\nCoba cek di HP kamu:\n1. Buka WhatsApp → grup Sentra\n2. Lihat daftar member — **+6281938953639** ada di list member?\n3. Kalau ada, coba kirim pesan biasa (bukan tag) di grup — text apa aja\n\nKalau nomor gateway nggak muncul di member list, berarti add-nya belum berhasil. WhatsApp kadang butuh nomor yang udah saved di kontak baru bisa di-add ke grup."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":154,"cacheRead":283895,"cacheWrite":269,"totalTokens":284319,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00385,"cacheRead":0.1419475,"cacheWrite":0.00168125,"total":0.14748375}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980789324}}
