{"type":"message","id":"28c9bb22","parentId":"2854a836","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:13:32.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHmm, kemungkinan WhatsApp-nya nggak bisa di-add ke grup karena:\n\n1. **Nomor gateway bukan nomor HP asli** — beberapa grup restrict hanya nomor yang terdaftar proper\n2. **Privacy settings** — nomor gateway mungkin di-set \"Nobody can add me to groups\"\n3. **Nomor belum di-save di kontak admin grup** — WhatsApp kadang block add kalau nomor belum saved\n\nAda workaround lain yang bisa kita pake:\n\n**Opsi 1: Invite link** — kalau grup punya invite link, gw bisa coba join lewat link (bukan di-add manual)\n\n**Opsi 2: Forward aja** — setiap habis meeting/diskusi di grup Sentra, kamu forward pesannya ke chat gw → gw process & summarize\n\n**Opsi 3: Screenshot/copy-paste** — kirim notes ke gw, sama efeknya\n\nHonestly opsi 2 atau 3 mungkin lebih practical buat sekarang. Kamu tinggal forward chat dari grup → gw auto-process, summarize, track action items, save ke Obsidian.\n\nMau coba invite link dulu, atau langsung pake forward approach?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":320,"cacheRead":284164,"cacheWrite":585,"totalTokens":285072,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.008,"cacheRead":0.14208199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00365625,"total":0.15375324999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980798938}}
{"type":"message","id":"627db6cd","parentId":"28c9bb22","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:13:32.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hmm, kemungkinan WhatsApp-nya nggak bisa di-add ke grup karena:\n\n1. **Nomor gateway bukan nomor HP asli** — beberapa grup restrict hanya nomor yang terdaftar proper\n2. **Privacy settings** — nomor gateway mungkin di-set \"Nobody can add me to groups\"\n3. **Nomor belum di-save di kontak admin grup** — WhatsApp kadang block add kalau nomor belum saved\n\nAda workaround lain yang bisa kita pake:\n\n**Opsi 1: Invite link** — kalau grup punya invite link, gw bisa coba join lewat link (bukan di-add manual)\n\n**Opsi 2: Forward aja** — setiap habis meeting/diskusi di grup Sentra, kamu forward pesannya ke chat gw → gw process & summarize\n\n**Opsi 3: Screenshot/copy-paste** — kirim notes ke gw, sama efeknya\n\nHonestly opsi 2 atau 3 mungkin lebih practical buat sekarang. Kamu tinggal forward chat dari grup → gw auto-process, summarize, track action items, save ke Obsidian.\n\nMau coba invite link dulu, atau langsung pake forward approach?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774980812125}}
