{"type":"message","id":"ea7c2d03","parentId":"1bebc7fb","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:49:15.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🔥 **Dispatched Uriel** → AI Character Generator\n\nYang bakal ada:\n- 🤖 **\"AI Generate Character\"** button di character sheet\n- Ketik deskripsi: *\"sneaky halfling rogue from the streets\"* → AI bikin full character\n- Auto-fill semua field: species, class, background, ability scores, name, backstory, appearance, equipment\n- Player bisa review & edit sebelum save\n- **Quick presets**: 🎲 Random, ⚔️ Warrior, 🔮 Mage, 🗡️ Rogue, 🛡️ Tank, 💚 Healer\n- Loading animation: *\"Summoning your character from the void...\"* ✨\n\nTunggu ~5-10 min."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":198,"cacheRead":375413,"cacheWrite":1273,"totalTokens":376885,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.00495,"cacheRead":0.1877065,"cacheWrite":0.00795625,"total":0.20061774999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774982946805}}
