{"type":"message","id":"41f5b4ae","parentId":"d6337ef8","timestamp":"2026-03-31T19:23:15.784Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHmm, Paul Simulator udah cukup loaded sih. Tapi kalau mau push further:\n\n**🎨 Visual & Polish:**\n1. **Dark/Light Theme Toggle** — some players prefer light mode\n2. **Animated Dice 3D Models** — upgrade dari CSS ke WebGL dice (three.js)\n3. **Character Portrait AI Generator** — ketik deskripsi → AI generate gambar character (pake image generation API)\n\n**📱 Social & Multiplayer:**\n4. **In-Game Chat** — text chat antar player di dalam app (bukan cuma dice broadcast)\n5. **Spectator Mode** — orang bisa nonton session tanpa jadi player\n6. **Session Replay** — playback seluruh session kayak nonton recording\n\n**🧠 AI-Powered:**\n7. **AI Rules Lawyer** — tanya \"how does grapple work?\" → AI jawab with rules reference\n8. **AI Quest Generator** — DM input setting → AI generate full quest (objectives, encounters, NPCs, rewards, plot twists)\n9. **AI Trap/Puzzle Generator** — generate puzzles + riddles buat dungeon\n\n**📊 Analytics:**\n10. **Player Stats Dashboard** — grafik: damage dealt over time, dice roll distribution, most used spells, kill count\n11. **Session Analytics** — durasi, jumlah rolls, combat vs roleplay ratio\n\n**🌐 Beyond the Table:**\n12. **Export to PDF** — character sheet as printable PDF\n13. **Share Character Card** — generate shareable image card of your character\n14. **Campaign Calendar** — in-world date tracker, schedule events\n\n**🏆 Engagement:**\n15. **Daily Quests** — mini challenges: \"Roll 3 Nat 20s today\", \"Use 5 different spells\"\n\nHonestly though — yang udah ada sekarang itu udah lebih dari cukup buat D&D night. Mungkin lebih baik **polish & test** dulu sebelum nambah fitur baru? Fix bugs, test semua flow end-to-end, pastiin mobile works smooth.\n\nAtau ada fitur spesifik dari list di atas yang kamu mau?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","m